      "text": "Un no to Israēta Behrnu\npuſs Teefas / ko Mohsus bij dal-\nlijis no teem Wihreem/ kas Kar-\nkā bij kawufchees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta patti puſs Teefa tahs\nDraudses bija no teem tihkeemi\nLohpeem / trihsreisi fimts tuhſ-\nſtoschi / un trihsdefinitis ſeptin\ntuhſtoschi un peez fimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Unto Wehrſchu bija trihs-\ndefinitis ſech tuhſtoschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Ehsetu bija trihs-\ndefmits tuhſtoschi un peezfimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Zilweku Dwehjelu\nbija ſechpademits tuhſtoschas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus nehme no\ntahs puſs Teefas to Israēta\nBehrnu/ weenu Saguhstitu no\npeezdefmiteem/ no Zilwekeem un\nLohpeem/ un dewe tohs teem Le-\nwiteem/ kas ta KUNGA Dsh-\nwokli ſargaja/ ittin ka tas Klings\nMohsum bij pawehlejis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad peegahje pee Mohsus\ntee Wirfneeki / tee ſkaititi/ kas\npahr ta Karra-Spehka tuhſto-\nscheem bija/un tee Wirfneeki pahr\nſinteen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſazzija us Mohsu:\nTawi Kalpi irr ſkaitijufschi to\nPulku/ to Karra-Wihro / kas\nappakſch muhfahm Rohkahm bi-\njufschi irr / un tur ne truhſst no\nnuuns neweens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 50,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz eﬀam mehs tam\nKUNGAM weenu Appuri at-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Mohsus un\nEeleasars tas Preesteris/ to Sel-\ntu no teem/ wiﬀadus labbi istai-\nfitus Rihkus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſs tas Pazelfcha-\nnas Selts/ ko tee tam KUN-\nGAM- pazehle/ bija feſchpadet-\nmits tuhſtoschi/ ſeptinfimts/ un\npeezdefmits Sihketi / no tee-\nWirfnekeem pahr tuhſtoscheem\nun no teem Wirfnekeein pal-\nſinteen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee Karra-Wihri bij-\nlaupiufschi ikweens preekich fer-\npafcha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 54,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Mohsus un\nEeleasars tas Preesteris to Sel-\ntu no teem Wirfnekeem pahr\ntuhſtoscheem/ un pahr ſimteen-\nun neffe to Sa-eefchanas Telti-\npar Peeminneschannu preekſch tee-\nIsraēta Behrneem/ ta KUNG-\nPreekſcha.\n"
    }
  ],
